products.title: Rattan Stacking Outdoor Chair in Brown
products.description:
The brown coloured synthetic wicker is more durable and easier to maintain than actual wicker because it won't wear out or fade as quickly. This is especially useful for outdoor use when the chairs are exposed to bright sun or light rain showers.
Ideal for those winter months when not in use - stacking saves space and keeps things ready for when the sun does appear again.

products.title: Black Steel Patterned Square Bistro Table
products.description:
This attractive steel patterned bistro table comes finished in black and measures 700mm square.
The robust construction and weather resistance makes this table ideal for use on patios, terraces and other outdoor areas.
It is easy to clean, sturdy and robust which is perfect for bistros and cafes whether used indoors or outside.

products.title: Foldaway Utility Chairs Black
products.description:
These robust, comfortable black folding chairs are ideal for buffets and party functions as they are easy to store and transport.
Suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, these chairs are ideal for use outside bars, restaurants and Cafes as they can be quickly folded flat to save space whilst being easy to clean.

Designed for use with Boleros folding table range, these hard wearing chairs are the perfect choice for any catering enterprise.
